@3532:I agree and I appreciate your vision of what this community should be. I do have to ask your and God's forgiveness, because at the current moment, my real life has been devastated by the pandemic. So are the real lives of my friends' and colleagues'.<br>
<br>
It's hard for me to get into a mood of penning quality contents. All I want right now is the total and complete collapse of that evil communist regime, so God's wrath can be soothed and we can go back to normal living.
